PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {
  fb:m.0dtfn fb:film.film.starring ?starring .
  ?starring fb:film.performance.character ?luke ; fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?luke rdfs:label 'Luke Skywalker' @en .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?invention WHERE {
  ?invention fb:common.topic.notable_types ?type .
  ?type rdfs:label 'Invention' @en .
  ?invention ?property fb:m.07bty
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?leader WHERE {
  fb:m.09c7w0 fb:government.us_president ?leader .
  ?leader fb:time.interval.start ?startDate .
  ?leader fb:time.interval.end ?endDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate <= '1945-09-02' ^^ xsd:date && ?endDate >= '1939-09-01' ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?leonardo ( COUNT( ?p ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?leonardo rdfs:label 'Leonardo da Vinci' @en .
  ?leonardo ?p ?o .
}
GROUP BY ?leonardo
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?work ?workLabel WHERE {

  ?work rdfs:label ?workLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?workLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?event ?eventLabel ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.0jnq8 fb:sports.sports_team.participated_in ?event .
  ?event rdfs:label ?eventLabel .
  ?event fb:sports.sports_event.year ?year .
  FILTER regex( ?eventLabel , "playoff|championship" , "i" )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 1

}

}
